    <h1 id = "next_implementazioni"> History of the project </h1>

    <p> Thanks to the determination of the volunteers, what seemed like a dream of freedom, found the support of several people and finally the support of programmers, analysts, mathematicians, graphic designers and responsible citizens is 
succeeded in trace a path for Eiresis to start in January 2013. </p>

    <p> Following are the salient events that allowed the birth of the project: </p>
