<div class = "slide green">
  <div class = "row centered">
    <h2> May 2013 - Version 3.0 </h2>
    <Ul>
      <li> Introduced forums for each group with a mailing list like feature! </li>
      <li> Removed elections feature </li>
      <li> New proposals list design with more filters and search tools </li>
      <li> Introduced gamification and user statistics </li>
      <li> @cite feature in proposal discussions with anonimity activated </li>
      <li> Redesign of propsoal creation wizard </li>
      <li> Improved proposal editing </li>
      <li> New RichTextEditor! Now we use CKEditor instead of TinyMCE </li>
      <li> New groups wall with information about recent activities </li>
      <li> Added possibilty to comment events and like other people comments </li>
      <li> Revised tutorials for new users </li>
      <li> You can now synchronize the calendar group with your Google Calendar </li>
      <li> RSS Atom Feed for blogs and groups </li>
    </ Ul>
  </div>
</div>
<div class = "slide violet">
  <div class = "row centered">
    <h2> May 2013 - Version 2.0 </h2>
    <Ul>
      <li> Totally renewed graphics! </li>
      <li> Free management of the paragraphs of the proposals </li>
      <li> Possibility to insert the contributions "in reference to a specific paragraph" </li>
      <li> Ability to indicate the contributions included during a text edit </li>
      <li> Visualization of the contributions included in the history of the proposal </li>
      <li> New visualization of the appreciation in the contributions and the possibility to modify one's own evaluation after the insertion of a suggestion </li>
      <li> Improved the service of e-mail notifications and in general the organization of notifications </li>
      <li> Ability to report a contribution as spam or indicate it as "not useful for discussion" </li>
      <li> Possibility to generate a pdf report of the proposal once it has been completed </li>
      <li> Caching mechanism for the most visited pages </li>
      <li> Many additional fixes and security checks </li>
      <li> Upload images for groups </li>
      <li> New feedback submission button </li>
    </ Ul>
  </div>
</div>
